  "双流区": "\n            \n            <section class=\"leading\"><p class=\"dao\"><i>导语</i> 2025年成都市23区县市小学毕业生初中入学划片范围公布啦，小编汇总如下，各位家长请注意查看。</p></section>\n            <div id=\"huodong-box-top\"></div>\n\n            <div class=\"youhui-box-top\"></div>\n\n            <div class=\"hot-hd-box\"></div>\n            \n            \n            <div class=\"content-box\" data-pswp-uid=\"1\">\n\t<p></p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t</p><p>\n\t\t\t　　<strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;\">2025年成都市双流区户籍初中一年级新生入学划片范围</span></strong>\n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t　　(↓点击图片可查看大图↓)\n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084203_32955.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084203_32955.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084215_54499.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084215_54499.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084223_83475.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084223_83475.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084228_46047.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084228_46047.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084233_49624.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084233_49624.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084238_40287.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084238_40287.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<center>\n\t\t\t<img class=\"img-responsive\" bigpicsrc=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084244_98139.png\" src=\"https://imgbdb4.bendibao.com/sl/600_0_/cdbdb/edu/20256/30/2025630084244_98139.png\">\n\t\t</center>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t　　温馨提示：\n\t\t</p>\n\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t　　初中一年级新生(含电脑随机录取到双流中学、棠湖中学的学生)入学报到注册时间为2025年7月10日、11日，届时请家长持户口簿原件及复印件1份(首页和学生本人页)前往对应学校报到注册。\n\t\t</p> \n \n\n            <div id=\"huodong-venue\" style=\"padding: 0px 20px;\"></div>\n\n                         </div>\n            <div class=\"youhui-box-top1\"></div>\n            <!-- <div class=\"tuijian-hd-box\"></div> -->\n            \n            \n<div id=\"add_ewm_content\" class=\"xuxian wenxintishi\">温馨提示：微信搜索公众号【成都本地宝升学】，关注后回复【初中划片】一键查询2025成都各中学对应片区范围（点击直达）、各区初中划片信息、最新升学安排等。</div>\n            <script>\n                if (navigator.userAgent.indexOf(\"baiduboxapp\") > -1 &&\n                    (window.location.href.indexOf(\"src_id\") > -1 ) &&\n                    document.getElementById(\"add_ewm_content\")\n                ) {\n                    document.getElementById(\"add_ewm_content\").style.display = \"none\";\n                }\n            </script>\n            <div class=\"pagination-with-title\"><section class=\"sec-list-heading\"><h2>分页导航</h2></section><ul><li><a href=\"199318.shtm\"> 第1页：2025年成都小升初划片范围汇总</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_2.shtm\">第2页：2025年成都高新区初中划片范围</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_3.shtm\">第3页：2025年成都市锦江区小学毕业生初中入学划片范围</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_4.shtm\">第4页：2025年青羊区小学毕业生初中入学划片范围</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_5.shtm\">第5页：2025年成都市金牛区小升初入学划片范围</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_6.shtm\">第6页：2025年成华区小升初划片范围一览表</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_7.shtm\">第7页：2025年武侯区初中入学划片范围</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_8.shtm\">第8页：2025年成都市温江区本地户籍初中一年级入学学区划片公告</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_9.shtm\">第9页：2025年成都市新都区小学毕业生初中入学划片范围公布</a></li><li><a href=\"199318_10.shtm\">第10页：2025年龙泉驿区公办初中入学划片范围一览表</a></li><li><a style=\"color:#f60;\" href=\"199318_1